# Resolution 2006-04-17.jpg.1: PostgreSQL Conference Insurance

This resolution was adopted by the Board of Directors of SPI at their
meeting of [April 18, 2006](/meetings/minutes/2006/2006-04-18/).

### It is resolved that:

1. The SPI treasurer and his designees are authorized to disburse CAD $2650
plus taxes for liability insurance for the PostgreSQL Anniversary Summit to be
held July 8-9, 2006.

2. The officers of SPI are authorized and directed to enter into reasonable
contractual agreements as necessary for the purposes of obtaining liability
insurance for this event.

